sentences: Rae Linda Brown (October 7, 1953 – August 20, 2017) was an American musicologist.
Brown wrote the groundbreaking biography, Heart of a Woman: The Life and Music of Florence B. Price, which was published in 2020.
Brown's 1987 dissertation focused on composer Florence Price.
